  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/dd25ef31c25dac2656435f31d42161ac.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=100 /></span>You are an unlikely hero going on an adventure across islands in the sky. It's dangerous to go alone - your trusty Book of Summons will keep you company. Day or night, sunshine or rain, explore each island your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/a615831e63919eee42ddfb9d6e45ccfe.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/33d681da69795e8b065ca0791be85974.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Collect and smash Crystals to add monsters to your party. Summon them in real-time, hack and slash battles. You don't need to rely on them to do all the fighting either. Armed with an enchanted sword, you can damage enemies to maximise summon time, and also heal and buff your summons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/381ba1d98fbd898a706722a1507fc4aa.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Upgrade player abilities with the items your've found on your travels. Take your pick from Vitality, Attack, Song, Essence, Magic and Spirit. Your Summons will grow when battling and become stronger through victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/d06b0fa5d9b89745d259e507fbe0fc47.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Meet new friends and other travellers to uncover the secrets of the seven floating islands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/51e8e832e3cb2f1a00dfe4675ba0c72f.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/dd25ef31c25dac2656435f31d42161ac.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=100 /></span>You are an unlikely hero going on an adventure across islands in the sky. It's dangerous to go alone - your trusty Book of Summons will keep you company. Day or night, sunshine or rain, explore each island your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/a615831e63919eee42ddfb9d6e45ccfe.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/33d681da69795e8b065ca0791be85974.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Collect and smash Crystals to add monsters to your party. Summon them in real-time, hack and slash battles. You don't need to rely on them to do all the fighting either. Armed with an enchanted sword, you can damage enemies to maximise summon time, and also heal and buff your summons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/381ba1d98fbd898a706722a1507fc4aa.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Upgrade player abilities with the items your've found on your travels. Take your pick from Vitality, Attack, Song, Essence, Magic and Spirit. Your Summons will grow when battling and become stronger through victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/d06b0fa5d9b89745d259e507fbe0fc47.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Meet new friends and other travellers to uncover the secrets of the seven floating islands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/51e8e832e3cb2f1a00dfe4675ba0c72f.avif?t=1747302100\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
